10 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Appropriation. There is appropriated $5.5 million from the general fund
11 to the department of public health and human services for each year of the biennium beginning July 1, 2025, for
12 the purposes of providing best beginnings child care scholarships to eligible child-care workers as provided in
13 [section 1].
14
15 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Effective date. [This act] is effective July 1, 2025.
